DISCIPLINARY CASES

2004-0790. In re Resignation of Cittadino.

IT IS ORDERED by this court, sua sponte, that Mary Elizabeth Cittadino, Attorney Registration No. 0074458, last known business address in West Chester, Ohio, is found in contempt for failure to comply with this court’s order of August 9, 2004, to wit: failure to surrender attorney registration card, surrender Certificate of Admission, and file affidavit of compliance on or before September 8, 2004.
